Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.29,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\alpha&H45&}轻轻呼唤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:36.29,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\alpha&H45&}黑暗中的乐园 是谎言还是梦境
